  02 Oct 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  add lppl 1.3c as license aswell

  29 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  switch to use versionned zips rather than tarballs

  27 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> files/texmf-update:
  run mktexlsr before generating language.dat file, this will prevent failures
  after merging texlive-basic

  26 Sep 2007; <alexis@gentoo.org> files/texmf-update:
  regenerate all formats like was done before, this will avoid having to
  manually update latex.fmt after adding more hyphenations support

  23 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> files/texmf-update:
  fix generation of language.dat when no other language than us is present

  22 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> files/texmf-update:
  no need to sync with tree updmap, texmf-update is now much faster

  22 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  mimic updmap syncwithtrees option to only ask for available fonts when
  installing texlive

  22 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  disable etex, we're using pdftex

  22 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  handle updmap.cfg

  22 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  make use of texlive-common eclass, include fontbin, rework included texmf
  handling, better handling of configurable files

  20 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  block xmltex, texlive provides it and may fail to install
  (http://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=419987)

  19 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  add a note about tests, disable em

  19 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  remove versionnator inherit, not needed

  19 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  drop virtual/x11 reference

  19 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  Use -j1 for emake only for icu-xetex, other parts are fine

  19 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  Use included icu, system one doesnt install necessary headers to be used
  with xetex

  19 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  remove libwww dep, not needed

  18 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  remove ncurses dep, only needed for dialog

  18 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  remove dep on media-libs/gd, only needed for dvipng

  18 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  -files/2007/texlive-core-2007-use-system-libtool.patch,
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  remove use system libtool hack, it is a bad idea to do that without running
  eautoreconf

  18 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  cleanup old stuff, esp. xdvik that we really dont want here, it would cause
  circular deps with t1lib and use doc

  17 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  remove dep on t1lib, only needed for xdvi and dvipng which are external

  17 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  fix icu include dir

  08 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  +files/2007/texlive-core-2007-icu-xetex-execstacks.patch,
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  fix exec stacks on xetex

  07 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  +files/2007/tetex-3.0_p1-xpdf-CVE-2007-3387.patch,
  texlive-core-2007.ebuild:
  import security fix from tetex

  05 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-source-2007.ebuild:
  add missing dep on fontconfig as reported by pchrist on freenode

  04 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-source-2007.ebuild:
  install dvipdfm from its own ebuild, install texmf-dist

  01 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-source-2007.ebuild:
  More verbose die messages, quote dir variables, patch by opfer

  01 Sep 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  +files/2007/tetex-3.0-CVE-2007-0650.patch, texlive-source-2007.ebuild:
  Add a patch from redhat for a buffer overflow in makeindex, see
  https://bugs.gentoo.org/show_bug.cgi?id=170861 and
  https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=225491

  29 Aug 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-source-2007.ebuild:
  Fix build with USE=doc, integrate binextra into this ebuild

  29 Aug 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-source-2007.ebuild:
  add some dies for mv's

  29 Aug 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org>
  texlive-source-2007.ebuild:
  add a changelog

